02:51:14.840 --> 02:51:22.520
[Guest]: built on something which is very simple, everyday stuff. And yet it makes you look at it and say,

02:51:22.520 --> 02:51:28.600
[Guest]: how come I didn't think of that one? You know, and that to me is in itself very, very interesting.

